# Root /convex/ existed temporarily in Milestone 2-3 when `convex dev` was
# initialized at repo root; it was relocated to packages/convex/convex/ during
# Milestone 3. Keep the ignore as a safety net against future accidental runs
# from repo root that would recreate it in the wrong place.
/convex/

# Trigger.dev tasks live at /src/trigger/ per trigger.config.ts `dirs: ["./src/trigger"]`.
# We DO track these files (they're implementation code). Only the _generated
# build output + caches get ignored.
# (No ignore rule here — the .trigger/ cache ignore higher up handles those.)
